name: CS353project
body:
### Introduction
In this project we will design and implement a data management system for a tourism agency. The system consists of customer, administrator and employee interfaces. Basically the system is used by customers and guests who are planning for a vacation or tour.

### Project Reports
All of the reports related with this project will be available at header section of this page.
